replyContent: An internet connection is not required at all times. The app needs to periodically check to make sure the software is not pirated. If you would like a refund for the app please feel free to email us at support@oceanhousemedia.com.

content: This book is ridiculously useful on car rides with my son, when it works. It is extremely irritating how I need to 'verify' the license for it through Wi-Fi. My son only has this for car rides, as its the only thing that keeps him from crying, so I am not near any Wi-Fi hotspots to verify the program, so most of the time it ends up being a very long car ride for us both. I don't get why I need to do this if I've already paid for the application?!
replyContent: An internet connection is not required at all times. The app needs to periodically check to make sure the software is not pirated. If you would like a refund for the app please feel free to email us at support@oceanhousemedia.com.
